{"tid":972791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陸軍中士愛慕英俊同袍，竟夜闖寢室忘情含他下體...","createTime":"2019-01-07T15:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T05:19:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3264b10b809bfc1bf833dac8c8df2a4107568d","tid":972791,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"陸軍又傳出性侵醜聞！陸軍金門防衛指揮部一名在機步連擔任中士班長的李姓男子，被同連康姓下士的英姿所吸引，竟然在105年8月時趁夜半時分潛入康男寢室，趁其熟睡時將他褲子拖下，直接含住康男下體，前後口交長達3分鐘，康男驚醒後發覺自己被班長猥褻，當場痛哭 。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，李男因愛慕康男已久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，在105年8月21日晚間11點左右，從自己的寢室潛入康男寢室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不顧一旁還有將近50位同袍在睡覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，就直接把康男的褲子脫掉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，並含住他的生殖器口交長達3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n而康男驚覺有異狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，起身一看發覺班長正含著自己的生殖器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當場嚇得趕快褲子拉起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，李男在事跡敗露後不慌不忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，還直接爬到床上向康男告白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，持續撫摸他的身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，並在臉頰旁吻了一下之後才離去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，康男此時已嚇到哭了出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n康男隔天早上隨即向督導長呈報此事，金門地院在開庭審理時，李男當庭承認罪行，並向康男致歉；法官認為，李男無前科，雖敗壞軍記且造成被害人心理創傷，但犯後態度尚知悔悟，法官在徵得康男同意後，依乘機性交罪輕判李男有期徒刑2年、緩刑5年，另需向公庫支付30萬元，本案仍可上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2664214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2664214&d=eWF3JVrZtYO%2BsRPnNlRqMIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=336375be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2664214&h=78086bb9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2664214</a>"},{"pid":"692563808711aaf77845aa1183b02696a537da5e","tid":972791,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:28:43.000Z","msg":"台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294282dd375faaf457d872bb64d43e1668813791","tid":972791,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:31:43.000Z","msg":"其實全世界都有呢類軍中強姦事件，大家唔好覺得太出奇"},{"pid":"928351196e35f9d7f11aebf51c8e6c0c9bdbfce7","tid":972791,"uid":157362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e911d4adc30165e049cdddb9eff910c3f215593","tid":972791,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87933ebae47b8fc68af163a77cae80358f0aaa26","tid":972791,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"當場痛哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47eb3f85b77727d88dbf331f07eb9b38b3d3793","tid":972791,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053a605d9f33f57d0fe37856ad19641dc0992e2e","tid":972791,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"射左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fb19190b6d40addfdcf7edf2dbee6cb77e89dc","tid":972791,"uid":176472,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-